@startuml KYC_Verification_States

' ============================================
' STATE DIAGRAM: KYC Verification Lifecycle
' Bug Bounty and Its Simulation Platform
' ============================================

title KYC Verification State Transitions

[*] --> Not_Started : User registers

Not_Started --> Documents_Pending : User initiates KYC
Documents_Pending --> Documents_Submitted : Upload ID documents
Documents_Submitted --> Under_Review : Submit for review

Under_Review --> Additional_Info_Required : Documents unclear/incomplete
Under_Review --> Approved : Documents valid
Under_Review --> Rejected : Documents invalid/fraudulent

Additional_Info_Required --> Documents_Submitted : Resubmit documents
Additional_Info_Required --> Expired : No response (14 days)

Approved --> Active : KYC verified
Rejected --> Documents_Pending : User can retry (max 3 attempts)
Rejected --> Permanently_Rejected : Max attempts exceeded

Active --> Expired : KYC expires (365 days)
Active --> Under_Reverification : Suspicious activity detected

Under_Reverification --> Active : Reverification passed
Under_Reverification --> Suspended : Reverification failed

Expired --> Documents_Pending : Renewal required
Suspended --> [*]
Permanently_Rejected --> [*]

note right of Documents_Submitted
  Required documents:
  - Government-issued ID
  - Proof of address
  - Selfie with ID
  - Tax identification (optional)
end note

note right of Under_Review
  Review process:
  - Manual verification by admin
  - Document authenticity check
  - Face matching
  - Address verification
  - Typical time: 24-48 hours
end note

note right of Approved
  Benefits:
  - Full platform access
  - Withdrawal enabled
  - Higher withdrawal limits
  - Participate in private programs
end note

note right of Active
  KYC validity:
  - Valid for 365 days
  - Renewal notification at 30 days
  - Auto-expire if not renewed
end note

note right of Under_Reverification
  Triggers:
  - Suspicious withdrawal patterns
  - Multiple failed withdrawals
  - Account sharing detected
  - Policy violation reports
end note

@enduml
